  <p>
    Changes since version 5.0b4:
    <itemize>
	<item> New features:
	<itemize>
	  <item> 'show pptp' and 'show l2tp' commands added.
	  </item>
	</itemize>
	</item>
	<item> Bugfixes:
	<itemize>
	  <item> Rewritten ippool to avoid races on IPCP renegotiation.
